data.description: Welcome to your new home in Northeast Philadelphia! With over 1,500 square feet, this spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.  As you approach, you'll be greeted by a large fenced-in front patio featuring a metal frame pergola with canopy cover – an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings or just relaxing in the fresh air.  Step through the enclosed foyer,  you'll be welcomed by a bright front sitting room with ample natural light . The charm continues into the generous living room, featuring original hardwood floors and a decorative fireplace.  The formal dining room sets the stage for memorable meals and gatherings. The updated eat-in kitchen is a chef's delight, offering granite countertops, contrasting cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. From the kitchen, step out onto the rear deck with a retractable awning, providing an ideal space for BBQs or simply enjoying the outdoors.  Ascending to the second floor, discover the main bedroom with an updated en-suite featuring a convenient shower stall with dual shower heads. Two additional spacious bedrooms,  an updated full hall bath with a shower/tub and convenient laundry chute, plus two hall closets complete the second-floor amenities.  The lower level surprises with a finished basement, complete with ceramic tile flooring, powder room, and a dedicated laundry area. Practical and stylish, this space offers additional room for entertainment or as a versatile flex space to suit your needs.  With the added benefit of an attached garage and additional alley parking, every aspect of your lifestyle is considered in this well-appointed townhome.  The location, backing up to Mullin Playground, ensures a delightful recreational space, while the close proximity to schools, shopping centers, and public transportation enhances the overall convenience.  Don't miss the chance to call this  NE Philadelphia gem your new home! Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of making it yours!
